msgid "SECTION 1"
msgstr "SECTION 1"

msgid "Information We Collect"
msgstr "Informations que nous collectons"

msgid "a. Account Information (if you sign in)"
msgstr "a. Informations du compte (si vous vous connectez)"

msgid ""
"If you create an account, we collect your <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">email address</strong> and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">name</strong>. This data is sent to our server (<strong "
"class=\"text-slate-700\">wird.me</strong>) to manage your session. "
"Authentication tokens are stored encrypted on your device only."
msgstr ""

msgid "b. Firebase Device Token (FCM)"
msgstr "b. Jeton d'appareil Firebase (FCM)"

msgid ""
"We use Firebase Cloud Messaging (by Google) to deliver push notifications. "
"An anonymous device token is generated by Firebase and sent to our server. "
"This token does not personally identify you, is used only to send "
"notifications, and is refreshed automatically by the OS."
msgstr ""
"Nous utilisons Firebase Cloud Messaging (de Google) pour envoyer des "
"notifications. Un jeton d'appareil anonyme est généré par Firebase et envoyé "
"à notre serveur. Ce jeton ne vous identifie pas personnellement et est "
"utilisé uniquement pour envoyer des notifications."

msgid "c. Contact Messages"
msgstr "c. Messages de contact"

msgid ""
"If you use the Contact Us feature, we receive the message you write and the "
"email you provide."
msgstr ""
"Si vous utilisez la fonctionnalité Nous contacter, nous recevons le message "
"que vous écrivez et l'adresse e-mail que vous fournissez."

msgid "SECTION 2"
msgstr "SECTION 2"

msgid "Data Stored Only on Your Device"
msgstr "Données stockées uniquement sur votre appareil"

msgid ""
"The following data is stored locally and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">never transmitted</strong>:"
msgstr ""

msgid "Reading progress, Khatmah plan, and Wird position"
msgstr "Progression de lecture, plan de Khatmah et position du Wird"

msgid "Azkar completion progress"
msgstr "Progression des Azkar"

msgid "Notification schedule and preferences"
msgstr "Calendrier et préférences de notifications"

msgid "Selected reciter and Mushaf style"
msgstr "Récitant et style de Mushaf sélectionnés"

msgid "Accessibility and display settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d'accessibilité et d'affichage"

msgid "Downloaded Mushaf images and audio files"
msgstr "Images du Mushaf et fichiers audio téléchargés"

msgid "The Quran database"
msgstr "La base de données du Coran"

msgid "SECTION 3"
msgstr "SECTION 3"

msgid "Microphone Access"
msgstr "Accès au microphone"

msgid ""
"If you enable the <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">Voice Commands</strong> "
"accessibility feature, the app uses your device microphone to recognise "
"spoken Arabic navigation commands."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"All voice processing happens locally on your device. No audio is sent to our "
"servers or any third party."
msgstr ""
"Tout le traitement vocal se fait localement sur votre appareil. Aucun audio "
"n'est envoyé à nos serveurs ou à des tiers."

msgid "SECTION 4"
msgstr "SECTION 4"

msgid "Third-Party Services"
msgstr "Services tiers"

msgid "Service"
msgstr "Service"

msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur"

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Objectif"

msgid "Push notifications"
msgstr "Notifications push"

msgid "App initialisation"
msgstr "Initialisation de l'application"

msgid "Subject to Google's Privacy Policy:"
msgstr "Soumis à la politique de confidentialité de Google :"

msgid "SECTION 5"
msgstr "SECTION 5"

msgid "Analytics and Crash Reporting"
msgstr "Analyses et rapports de pannes"

msgid ""
"This app does <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">not</strong> use Firebase "
"Analytics, Crashlytics, or any third-party analytics or advertising SDK. We "
"do not track your behaviour inside the app."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 6"
msgstr "SECTION 6"

msgid "Data Sharing"
msgstr "Partage des données"

msgid ""
"We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with third parties for "
"advertising or commercial purposes. Data is shared only with Firebase "
"(Google) as described in Section 4, which is required for push notification "
"delivery."
msgstr ""
"Nous ne vendons ni ne partageons vos données personnelles avec des tiers à "
"des fins publicitaires ou commerciales. Les données sont partagées "
"uniquement avec Firebase (Google) pour l'envoi de notifications."

msgid "SECTION 7"
msgstr "SECTION 7"

msgid "Data Security"
msgstr "Sécurité des données"

msgid ""
"Authentication tokens are stored using platform-level encrypted storage "
"(Android Keystore)."
msgstr ""
"Les jetons d'authentification sont stockés dans un espace de stockage "
"chiffré au niveau de la plateforme (Android Keystore)."

msgid "All communication with our server uses HTTPS."
msgstr "Toutes les communications avec notre serveur utilisent HTTPS."

msgid "SECTION 8"
msgstr "SECTION 8"

msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Vos droits"

msgid ""
"If you have created an account, you may request access to or deletion of "
"your data through the <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">Contact Us</strong> "
"screen inside the app."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 9"
msgstr "SECTION 9"

msgid "Audience"
msgstr "Public cible"

msgid ""
"This app is designed to be suitable for a general audience. It contains no "
"adult content, no violence, and no advertising."
msgstr ""
"Cette application est conçue pour convenir à un public général. Elle ne "
"contient ni contenu pour adultes, ni violence, ni publicité."

msgid "SECTION 10"
msgstr "SECTION 10"

msgid "Changes to This Policy"
msgstr "Modifications de cette politique"

msgid "We may update this policy from time to time. The \\"
msgstr ""

msgid "Wird App"
msgstr "Application Wird"

